  <brief_title>High Sensitive Troponin T (hsTnT) and Copeptin as Prognostic Parameters in Patients With Elective Total Endoprosthesis</brief_title>
  <official_title>High Sensitive Troponin T (hsTnT) and Copeptin as Prognostic Parameters in Patients With Elective Knee and Hip Endoprosthesis</official_title>
